It seems as though I have ran across your guild leader and her servant the other night within the shadowed protection of Dear Shar Vahl. I was quite impressed with not only thier honor and nobility, but also thier grasp of the Vah SHir Language. they must truly be accepted within Shar Vahl's gates to be such.<br>
<br>
There is an Order forming.. even now as we speak within the confines of Shar Vahl. a group of Vah Shir along with the aid of a noble Northman and a Elven Holy Warrior. This group seeks those that would protect that which is pure and noble in all living things. and bring to justice those that seek to bring darkness across the land, not only upon Luclin, but Norrath as well. Would the Court be such a  devout group?<br>
<br>
I do hope so. I wish to speak to you once again Good Enchantress, if ever close to the fabled walls of Shar Vahl please send for me... for I believe that you and I may be able to form such an alliance to help protect what we both hold dear and true to our hearts and souls.<br>
<br>
Aberian the Brave<br>
Khala Dun... Warrior.. and Adventurer<br>
